{"id": "1204373884355223572", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 0, "author_id": "428893539561373726", "author_name": "chennnn328", "author_bot": false, "content": "螺旋保留變成50%\n一個隊伍用1000血量來算的話\n最多可以保留20%最大血量\n也就是下回合最多拿200盾\n那這樣我前一回合只要疊400就可以吃到上限\n改成這樣對盾毒或是盾反應該都算蠻不錯用的", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:31:50.215000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1204374578613456906", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "校猫有没有兴趣正好增强一下海之梦呢（", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:34:35.739000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1204374578361663548", "filename": "IMG_7855.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 212265, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1204366577877782528/1204374578361663548/IMG_7855.png?ex=69ccf4bb&is=69cba33b&hm=1fbd44c96a07d0a5cf1c215d7055efc56e86e6e42e31846bff7dc24b9b242187&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1204374659454210058", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 19, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得螺旋改動後對一般隊伍也會好用非常多，能在boss不攻擊的回合使防禦卡能也有一半的收益，大幅降低牌順太過噁心的情況", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:34:55.013000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["428893539561373726"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1204373884355223572", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1204374894884954112", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 19, "author_id": "428893539561373726", "author_name": "chennnn328", "author_bot": false, "content": "例如潘 或是鼠鼠這種會被打+傷害的", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:35:51.144000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["392840163732226058"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1204374659454210058", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1204374983309000714", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 0, "author_id": "428893539561373726", "author_name": "chennnn328", "author_bot": false, "content": "前一回合可以爆發疊盾\n下回合比較沒壓力", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:36:12.226000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1204375144508694528", "channel_id": "1204366577877782528", "type": 0, "author_id": "428893539561373726", "author_name": "chennnn328", "author_bot": false, "content": "的確 這樣改會讓這命輪可以用在很多隊伍上面\n莉莉隊應該也有搞頭", "timestamp": "2024-02-06T10:36:50.659000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1204366577877782528", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅V1.2下篇「遊戲性」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
